==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
Pinyin: biǎoyǎn (biao3 yan3)
===[[Min Nan]]===
[[POJ]]: piáu-ián
===Cantonese===
Jyutping:

===Etymology===
From [[表]] ("show, "express," "manifest," "display") + [[演]] ("perform," "put on")

===Noun===
'''[[表]][[演]]''' (simplified and traditional)

# performance; exhibition

===Verb===
'''[[表]][[演]]''' (simplified and traditional)

# to perform; to act; to play
# to demonstrate

===Related terms===
*[[演奏]] (yǎnzòu) (to play an instrument)

